{"tid":2478591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女童送畫像 林卓廷︰感激大家心意","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:36:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f0e2e32ce2b152d6718194635d97c53617c2e6","tid":2478591,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/QV7CC4HTZJCVZCPNXYJAUZRKUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FQV7CC4HTZJCVZCPNXYJAUZRKUE%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=cb03d4f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FQV7CC4HTZJCVZCPNXYJAUZRKUE%2F&h=11b02862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/QV7CC4HTZJCVZCPNXYJAUZRKUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n女童送畫像 林卓廷︰感激大家心意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-L9GisSAd0zjr6DQMOsolhQth1A=/510x433/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QMILI3PTTZA2NGPRJGQ3OBHCPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-L9GisSAd0zjr6DQMOsolhQth1A%3D%2F510x433%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQMILI3PTTZA2NGPRJGQ3OBHCPA.jpg&h=24b7c715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一名女童繪畫林卓廷畫像送到灣仔街站。林卓廷fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】47名民主派因參加初選被控串謀顛覆國家政權罪，僅11人獲保釋。各還柙人士親友風雨不改到監獄及收押所探望，牆外友人則為牆內人設街站打氣。林卓廷團隊昨最後一天設街站收集市民心意卡，獲女童送贈親繪的林卓廷畫像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「睇唔到將來」長毛無意寫回憶錄<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷黨友及助理連日擺街站聲援，林的fb小編前日上載一張圖畫，題為「泡菜妹妹畫林卓廷」，是一名女童親筆繪畫，再送到灣仔街站。林透過妻子表示：「收到大量市民的心意卡，我請她全數寄給我，我會逐一細看&hellip;&hellip;大家的心意，我們一家都收到，非常感激，請繼續支持其他牆內朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n已還柙逾200天的快必譚得志，其團隊於fb上載「還押日誌」。快必指，周日首次與梁國雄「放風」，「佢話當以為日日嘅安排係一樣，但係時不時又會有些意外驚喜」。其間長毛提到有人建議他寫回憶錄，惟長毛認為，「都睇唔到將來，寫回憶錄都冇用」，快必回應，「我哋面臨種種嚴峻挑戰，但仍然要保存住『盼望』」。<br />\n<br />\n快必不忘回覆支持者來信，有人祝願他「早日回復自由」，快必表示：「我在想如果我一直沒有自由，大家可以繼續支持我幾耐呢？我又想，如果我回復自由，但係戴耀廷教授同其他人都未有自由，咁我又應作何事呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NdDVcUVd20NbMopfwUM_NTKmMoA=/510x382/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KPFF3CJ5WRFOLB3AI5KIAF4AII.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNdDVcUVd20NbMopfwUM_NTKmMoA%3D%2F510x382%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKPFF3CJ5WRFOLB3AI5KIAF4AII.jpg&h=30af12b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林卓廷黨友及助理連日擺街站聲援。"},{"pid":"eb62edaf3434e02808042f877b5dd787b3127eee","tid":2478591,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0d33633d3e0a44eef069a84fb30c94800131e1","tid":2478591,"uid":160193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"對眼畫得最似(三白眼)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}